[4] Florida (Broward County)
Date: Sat 14 Apr 2012
Source: Local 10 [edited]
http://www.local10.com/thats-life/health/Pertussis-identified-in-Broward-Co/-/1717022/10808020/-/lns7waz/-/


Four cases of pertussis, or whooping cough, were identified in Broward County this week, health officials said. The health department said 3 young children and one adult had confirmed cases. Since the beginning of 2012, several counties throughout the state have reported higher levels of pertussis.

